casebody.data:
Wednesday, September 25, 1991

MERIT DOCKET

91-651. Alexander v. Rush.

Clark County, No. 2791. On motion for stay, motion to accelerate, and request for oral argument. Motions and request denied. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
